snippet.title: Scott The Woz
snippet.description:
Hey all, Scott here.

Scott The Woz is a comedic video game centric variety show that focuses on reviews, editorials, retrospectives, and much, much more. New episodes are uploaded every Sunday night (EST).

Other original content, mainly comedic shorts, can be found here as well. New originals are uploaded sporadically.

"Scott The Woz" Logo/Banner by Nico Vliek (@WhaddupNico)
